        "title": "fix(ollama): strip inline kimi cloud reasoning leak",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add Ollama Kimi-cloud response sanitizer for leaked inline reasoning prefixes in visible assistant text\n- scope sanitizer to `kimi-k*:cloud` and boundary-delimited payloads only, with conservative guards to avoid clipping normal output\n- add regression coverage in Ollama stream runtime tests\n\n## Changes\n- `extensions/ollama/src/stream.ts`\n  - added `stripKimiInlineReasoningFromVisibleText(...)`\n  - invoke sanitizer from `buildAssistantMessage(...)` before publishing visible `text` blocks\n- `extensions/ollama/src/stream-runtime.test.ts`\n  - new test: strips inline reasoning prefix for `kimi-k2.6:cloud`\n  - new test: does not strip boundary marker for non-Kimi models\n\n## Validation\n- local focused run previously passed on the working tree:\n  - `pnpm -s vitest run extensions/ollama/src/stream-runtime.test.ts`\n  - result: `1 file passed, 84 tests passed`\n- clean worktree rerun in this environment timed out under repeated plugin timing output before completion.\n\n## Live behavior proof status\n- CLI proof attempts were run in this runtime via `ollama run ... --think false` for both:\n  - `kimi-k2.6:cloud`\n  - `kimi-k2.5:cloud`\n- both returned:\n  - `403 Forbidden: this model requires a subscription, upgrade for access`\n- proof artifacts captured at:\n  - `/tmp/issue-86129-proof/cli-baseline.txt`\n  - `/tmp/issue-86129-proof/kimi-k26-think-false.full.txt`\n  - `/tmp/issue-86129-proof/kimi-k25-think-false.full.txt`\n\nFixes #86129\n",
